      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARRA LAD (4) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4 lengths (18.01) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Has ability and can bounce back. WATCH HER WIN (1) hit the ground running and on speed early but faded out of it to finish fourth (22.75) at Gosford over 388m. Form here at this distance is sound. Worth another chance. OUT THE WILL (6) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.50 beating White High. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Must be included in calculations. BUGLE GIRL (2) deserves plenty of thought over this trip.",
